-- out/todo.txt --
cyclicError: v3 reports improved error message vs v2.
nestedWithDynamicFieldOK: fixed bug in v3 (was incorrect in v2).
v3 uses structure sharing (~) for several fields.
issue3729.withoutDisjunction: error in v3 has fewer position annotations than v2.
issue3729.withoutDisjunctionWithEmbed, withEmbed.incomplete: v3 leaks the embedded _ from the comprehension body into the null optional constraint, causing null to appear as an embedded value in root.
embed.fail1/fail4: errors have different position annotations in v3 vs v2.
